results.title: Basic Jeans
results.description: A pair of classic blue jeans features a straight leg and a mid-rise waistline. Made from durable denim fabric, they are designed to be comfortable and long-lasting. The jeans feature five pockets, including a coin pocket, and are fastened with a zipper and button at the waist. The blue color of the denim is a timeless classic that can be dressed up or down for any occasion.

results.title: Red Day Off
results.description: A pair of jeans with a red color can add a bold and vibrant touch to your outfit. The jeans are made of a sturdy denim material with a red dye that has been applied to the fabric. The jeans have a classic five-pocket design with metal rivets and a zip fly. The red color can range from a deep burgundy to a bright cherry red, depending on the shade of the dye used. The jeans can be styled with a simple white t-shirt and sneakers for a casual look or dressed up with heels and a blouse for a more elevated outfit.

results.title: Social Green
results.description: These microfiber pants in a rich shade of green offer both comfort and style. The fabric is lightweight and breathable, perfect for a day out or a casual gathering. The slim fit and tapered leg create a flattering silhouette, while the classic five-pocket design and zip-fly with button closure provide a timeless look. Dress them up with heels or keep it casual with sneakers. Either way, these pants are a versatile addition to any wardrobe.

results.title: Social Green Two
results.description: Step up your denim game with these stylish green jeans. Made from high-quality denim, these jeans are durable and comfortable for all-day wear. The slim fit design and flattering cut will accentuate your curves and make you feel confident and fashionable.

results.title: Casual Orange
results.description: These jeans pants in a vibrant orange hue are the perfect addition to your casual wardrobe. Made with high-quality denim fabric, they feature a classic five-pocket design and a comfortable mid-rise waist. The slim-fit cut flatters your figure, while the ankle-length hem is perfect for showcasing your favorite footwear.

results.title: Flat Gray
results.description: The classic and versatile nature of jeans makes them available in a wide variety of colors, including gray. Gray jeans can be a great addition to any wardrobe, as they can be dressed up or down depending on the occasion. They pair well with a range of colors, including black, white, and other neutrals.

results.title: Garden Vibes
results.description: Cotton pants with floral patterns are a great way to add a pop of color and femininity to your outfit. They can be worn in a casual or dressy setting, depending on how you style them. When pairing them with tops, it's best to stick with solid colors to avoid clashing.

results.title: Yellow Yep
results.description: A pair of jeans pants with a yellow color can be a great choice for a fun and vibrant look. Yellow is a bright and cheerful color that can add a pop of sunshine to any outfit. A classic blue denim jean with yellow accents, such as yellow stitching or yellow patches, can create a unique and stylish look.

results.title: Flat Brown
results.description: A pair of jeans pants with a brown color can be a great choice for a classic and versatile look. Brown is a neutral color that pairs well with a variety of other colors and styles. A classic blue denim jean with brown accents, such as brown stitching or brown patches, can create a unique and stylish look.

results.title: Basic Casual Black
results.description: A pair of black jeans is a versatile and timeless addition to any wardrobe. Black jeans can be dressed up or down, making them a great choice for a variety of occasions. A classic style with a slim or straight leg can provide a sleek and sophisticated look, while distressed or ripped black jeans can add an edgy touch.

results.title: Basic T-Shirt
